{"tid":1574378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廉署起訴一名警員　涉欺詐女子共9萬多元貸款及手錶","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T12:13:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcce5b268739ae745e49dda571be030651ce412","tid":1574378,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"廉署落案起訴一名警員，控告他涉嫌欺詐一名女子20筆共9萬多元的貸款及一隻價值超過6萬元的手錶，以及妨礙司法公正，要求對方不要再跟進向廉署作出的投訴。被告星期三在西九龍裁判法院答辯，獲准保釋等待應訊。<br />\n<br />\n廉署接獲警方轉介的貪污投訴，揭發有關罪行。25歲被告張永亭被控3項欺詐及一項妨礙司法公正。他案發時是警員，2015年認識一名女子，被控涉嫌於2015年至2016年期間，向對方訛稱自己急需籌錢以償還按揭及汽車貸款，以及籌措醫藥費治療腦內血塊，意圖詐騙事主提供貸款。<br />\n<br />\n張永亭又涉嫌在2017年聲稱轉行擔任倫敦金銷售員，訛稱工作關係需要穿戴名貴手錶，誘使事主購買手錶，其後涉嫌致電事主，要求及誘使她不再跟進向廉署投訴的欺詐指控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480881-20190916.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480881-20190916.htm&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbbO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=51e2f086\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480881-20190916.htm&h=ba23d39c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480881-20190916.htm</a>"},{"pid":"18805db2d07bec5c083ff30a975e4dc1263d6a61","tid":1574378,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4226dc7ece179779865625c14e90b80a987762d0","tid":1574378,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"元朗單野呢？"},{"pid":"98550170633b0a77e4088ce9843ef0b12db05e57","tid":1574378,"uid":20209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"警犬果然係倫敦狗水平"},{"pid":"4630e989834c7b3a48f3fba3cbd40a3b815f3422","tid":1574378,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg